title: Luke Combs Performs In Studio + Our All-Time Favorite Country Songs + Will Lunchbox Get A Haircut For Raymundo’s Wedding?
itunes:title: Luke Combs Performs In Studio + Our All-Time Favorite Country Songs + Will Lunchbox Get A Haircut For Raymundo’s Wedding?
description:
Luke Combs comes in to perform, talks CMA nominations and about his new deluxe album. Bobby has everyone share their favorite country song of all-time. Plus, we check in one last time with Raymundo before his wedding this weekend to see if Lunchbox plans to cut his crazy hair before the service!
